column3: Now equipped with seventh-generation Intel Core processors, Laptop is snappier than ever. From daily tasks like launching apps and opening files to more advanced computing, you can power through your day thanks to faster SSDs and Turbo Boost processing up to 3.6GHz.

The Logitech M185 Wireless Optical Mouse is a great device for any computer user, and as Logitech are the global market leaders for these devices, you are also guaranteed absolute reliability. A mouse to be reckoned with!
